HEADWORD: Fennec
<hw>Fen"nec</hw> <pr>(f⟦ecr⟧n"n⟦ecr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar.
<ets>fanek</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small, African,
